entries.MST_FRONTIERHUNTER_UNIQUEREWARD_516_COMM: You're here! The area to be surveyed this time is full of tough enemies, but I'm sure you can take care of them! Do your best to get your hands on some of those great Summoners' Hall rewards!
entries.MST_FRONTIERHUNTER_UNIQUEREWARD_5_COMMEN: The way things are now, your Hunter Rank will increase by 1 after everything's over. However you can always aim a bit higher! Let's try it again! Come on, fight!
entries.MST_FRONTIERHUNTER_UNIQUEREWARD_600_COMM: Wow, you're the best! Keep this up and your rank could instantly increase by 5! But other Summoners are trying their best as well, so don't get careless!
entries.MST_FRONTIERHUNTER_UNIQUEREWARD_601_COMM: Amazing! At this rate, your rank could increase by 4! Ah, but it looks like there are some other Summoners on your heels! Hold on just a little bit longer!
entries.MST_FRONTIERHUNTER_UNIQUEREWARD_602_COMM: I knew you had it in you! Keep this up and your Hunter Rank will increase by 3! But surely you're aiming higher than this, right? I'm cheering for you!
